		# w/a		1428 #     2 [97.1428]:   Enum can only be assigned to same enum type or enum member. 
	#RTL-waived
		1428 #       [97.1428]:   Enum can only be assigned to same enum type or enum member. 
		1689 #    26 [97.1689]:   Illegal combination of procedural and continuous assignment found for variable ( X ).
		1442 # 39055 [97.1442]:   Illegal use of struct/array literal within concatenation 
		1607 #   158 [97.1607]:   Incompatible assignment found, for structure array / structure / unpacked array. 
		1445 #    73 [97.1445]:   Illegal use of aggregate expression in this context.
	#SVA-waived
		1387 #     2 [97.1387]:   Deferred assertion action block must be a task enable only.
		1547 #    23 [97.1547]:   Looping statement can not contain concurrent assertion.
		1549 #    87 [97.1549]:   First statement of always block should be event control as it contains concurrent assertion.
#SRID REVISIT		811  #    88 [97.811] :   Object is of not valid type to be used in expression.
# 2nd iteration
		1390 #     5 [97.1390]:   Items within packages cannot have hierarchical references.
